headline: Aetna, a CVS Health company, receives Health Plan of the Year Award from Press Ganey
summary: Aetna®, a CVS Health® company (NYSE: CVS), today announced that Press Ganey recognized Aetna as its first-ever Health Plan of the Year at their annual Human Experience (HX26) Conference in Orlando, Florida. Press Ganey, the leading provider of experience measurement, data analytics and AI-powered insights to health systems and health plans, presented the award to Steve Nelson, president of Aetna.

headline: Cardinal Health Stock Jumps After Earnings. Its CEO Explains What Went Right.
summary: Less than a month after raising its fiscal-year outlook,  Cardinal Health  hiked it again.  The company, which distributes pharmaceuticals and other medical supplies to customers like  CVS Health  said Thursday that it now expects adjusted earnings in the range of $10.15 to $10.35 a share for the current fiscal year.  The new range also is above the $10.02 a share analysts are expecting, according to FactSet.

headline: CVS Health Helps Customers Accelerate Biosimilar Adoption Through Formulary Changes - Supporting Affordable Options for Osteoporosis Care
summary: CVS Health® (NYSE: CVS) today announced new steps to further help customers expand adoption of lower-cost biosimilar medications. Effective April 1, 2026, CVS Caremark will begin offering osteoporosis biosimilars Ospomyv and Stoboclo, as well as generic teriparatide, Bonsity, and Tymlos on major national commercial template formularies. headline: Aetna Launches Simplified, Digital-first, Benefits Onboarding Experience for Members in 2026
summary: Aetna®, a CVS Health® company (NYSE: CVS) today announces the introduction of an industry leading, fully-digital benefits onboarding experience for four million members during the 2026 welcome season. This technology-enabled offering provides easier navigation and self-service for members by leveraging digital and Rich Communication Services ["RCS"] enabled text messaging channels to access the information, resources and support they need at the start of the plan year.
